virtual void gaia::connectivity::GpsStatusListener::onGpsStatusChanged ( GpsStatusEvent  event) [virtual]

Called to report changes in the GPS status.

The event number is one of:

  • GpsStatus#GPS_EVENT_STARTED
  • GpsStatus#GPS_EVENT_STOPPED
  • GpsStatus#GPS_EVENT_FIRST_FIX
  • GpsStatus#GPS_EVENT_SATELLITE_STATUS

When this method is called, the client should call LocationManager#getGpsStatus to get additional status information.

Parameters:
eventevent number for this notification
